            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-anton text-white uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">
              Zona de <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-400 to-fuchsia-500">Torneos</span>
            </h1>

